{"tid":680463,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"理性嘅你有野想講，咪入黎講！","createTime":"2018-05-27T08:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T07:19:11.000Z","uid":111512,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"884c8e11267daf8d0d187bdcede052d0314aa8b9","tid":680463,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"其實我一直有個怪癖，就係好鐘意諗野。<br />\n仲係乜都諗一餐。但慢慢發現諗完又分享唔到好un住un住。<br />\n所以想係廣大既連登入面，搵同我一樣既「病態」人士一齊圍吓爐。<br />\n咩都可以講，一齊分享思想，睇係大家係點樣思考。（連登巴/絲打個腦唔係得性/淫野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n都係個句，有野想講咪講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n題目自訂，集思廣益，有知之士，不服來辯<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n附上三年前的「病態」實錄-拖鞋<br />\n<br />\n關於拖鞋<br />\n拖鞋，相比起那名貴波鞋，高跟鞋和皮鞋，顯然顯得他的價值低得無可再低<br />\n他不能登上漂亮舞台，又無法好好保護腳踝<br />\n因此，他，不會受到重視<br />\n就如你的名貴鞋，如有損害，甚至沾有半點污跡<br />\n你會感到可惜，唔開心<br />\n相反拖鞋，他價值低，他隨處可見，即便受到損害，換新便可<br />\n無人會覺得可惜<br />\n但仔細想想<br />\n正正因為他的價值低，他的隨處可見，可以讓你呼之則來，揮之則去<br />\n但同時陪伴著你<br />\n走過無數的路<br />\n也陪伴著你成長，見證著你由小腳成長成大腳<br />\n但你經常穿他的原因無它<br />\n只是因為方便<br />\n穿上不消一秒，除下同樣不消一秒<br />\n但你卻會為那些名貴鞋花上你人生的一分鐘去穿著它<br />\n但縱觀我的人生中<br />\n鞋是換了不少<br />\n但最經常著<br />\n最經得起潮流的的轉變<br />\n卻是那價值低得無可再低的拖鞋<br />\n<br />\n黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced605d593cd22904afa397997060cebfadcc7a3","tid":680463,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"寫呢篇野既時候，好似係做緊兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw pushhhhhhhbhhh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09cffd211a8e542afe12cc8af4b7bf0f04b8869","tid":680463,"uid":35777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ced605d593cd22904afa397997060cebfadcc7a3","tid":680463,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"寫呢篇野既時候，好似係做緊兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw pushhhhhhhbhhh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:35:56.000Z","msg":"愈簡單愈不受重視<br />\n依個世界嘅人太得閒"},{"pid":"792736528df616cf9eea8ddc68d81ae4918a875d","tid":680463,"uid":52984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"拖鞋就好似啲古代妾侍，好少人會帶出街，身價好低，比啲男人中出(唔着襪），但又心甘情願係你床邊服侍你。<br />\n<br />\n出街鞋好多都有名份，有屬於自己個櫃，甚至乎一啲名牌鞋會化妝，有人幫佢定期抹。但係呢啲text ultra boost 都係只係臭雞一隻，淨係識搵有錢仔埋單。對比之下冇拖鞋咁舒服。<br />\n<br />\n你一生人最鍾意嘅人未必係你長期陪伴嗰個，但係長期陪你嗰個，大部份人都唔會珍惜，着撚完就求其飛埋一邊。"},{"pid":"c5dedf08d73da6ab68badeff221a8248598c4fe9","tid":680463,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"加油咁多位"},{"pid":"c406250a5f468b91ecf0c86e10b6ee7604aebb1f","tid":680463,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d09cffd211a8e542afe12cc8af4b7bf0f04b8869","tid":680463,"uid":35777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ced605d593cd22904afa397997060cebfadcc7a3","tid":680463,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"寫呢篇野既時候，好似係做緊兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\